and is intended to be omitted in the law.

SB 1064 2
18 products, alternative nicotine products, or vapor products
19 to persons under twenty-one years of age.
20 3. The provisions of this section shall not be
21 construed to preempt any local laws, ordinances, orders,
22 rules, or regulations relating to tobacco products,
23 alternative nicotine products, or vapor products that are
24 enacted by a county, municipality, or other political
25 subdivision and that are in effect as of January 1, 2026.
26 Any such local law, ordinance, order, rule, or regulation
27 that is enacted or amended after January 1, 2026, shall be
28 subject to the provisions of this section.
